<div style=" text-align: center;" class="mb-5">
    <img src="~/Content/Images/BookLibrary.png" class="img-fluid mb-4" role="img" alt="BoolLibrary" />
    <h3>
        It gives a great opportunities to manage your personal library or public library. It can be used manage librarie, university librarie, private books collections, catalogs. Book library is functional and easy solution for libraries management that allows manage books, authors, categories of books.
    </h3>
</div>

<div id="demo" class="carousel slide my-5 justify-content-center" data-ride="carousel">

    <!-- Indicators -->
    <ul class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ul>

    <!-- The slideshow -->
    <div class="carousel-inner ">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/Library.png" style="height:400px" alt="Library" class="col-lg-6 mx-auto d-block col-sm-12" />
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/digital-library.png" style="height:400px"  alt="Library" class="col-lg-6 mx-auto d-block col-sm-12" />
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/school-library.png" style="height:400px"  alt="Library" class="col-lg-6 mx-auto d-block col-sm-12" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Left and right controls -->
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#demo" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#demo" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
    </a>

</div>
<div class="col-lg-12 col-sm-12 ">
    <h3 class="text-center">To date, we have gathered  many books from a variety of large catalogs as well as single contributions, with more on the way.</h3>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
    @Html.ActionLink("BOOKS", "Books", "Home", null, new { @class = "btn btn-outline-success btn-lg col-lg-6" })
</div>

